        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Metaphire nanaoensis. (A) Male pore region (sw, skin wall; sp, small pad); (B) caecum; (C) spermathecae (dv, diverticulum; amp, ampulla); (D) testis sacs and seminal vesicles (ts, testis sacs; sv, seminal vesicles); (E) prostate gland." ;
